<div class="row copy">
  <div class="small-12 small-centered columns">
    <p>Students will gain an understanding of the iOS App process by building fully functioning apps.  Each project will walk you step by step through development, starting with an empty project until that project is complete. Designed to give you a solid foundation, you will experience most of the components Apple provides as well as excellent third-party components. Additionally, you will have access to screencasts of the most popular 3rd party libraries and how to bring them into your app.</p>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered columns">
      <%= form_tag 'mailing_list/subscribe', method: 'POST', id: 'subForm', 'data-has-zcom-email-handler': 1 do %>
        <div class="input-group">
          <%= email_field_tag :email, nil, id: 'fieldEmail', placeholder: 'Enter your email here' %>
          <div class="input-group-button">
            <%= submit_tag "Subscribe", class: 'postfix button custom-button' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

